titleNullable: Nigeria Stock Exchange All Share Index
subtitleNullable: Data on All Share Index of Nigeria Stock Exchange from 2008 - 2020
descriptionNullable:
The Nigerian Stock Exchange (NSE) now Nigerian Exchange Group is a Nigerian stock exchange founded in 1961 in Lagos. As of November 2020, it has a total of 177 listed companies.
The All-Share Index tracks the general market movement of all listed equities on Nigerian Exchange, including those listed on the Growth Board, regardless of capitalization.
